-- Assad Tells Russia He’s Committed to Ending Violence in Syria
-- B y   B r a d   C o o k
-- 2012-02-07T13:05:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-07/assad-tells-russia-he-s-committed-to-ending-violence-in-syria.html
Syrian President Bashar al-Assad is
committed to ending all violence in his country, Russian Foreign
Minister Sergei Lavrov said after talks in Damascus today,
according to a pool report from Russian news service Itar-Tass.  Russia’s position is to use a plan put forward by the  Arab
League  to end the bloodshed in  Syria , Lavrov said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brad Cook at 
 bcook7@bloomberg.net  